        -: 3878:the input string may optionally be prefixed with C<"0b"> or plain C<"b">
        -: 3879:
        -: 3880:=item For C<grok_hex>
        -: 3881:
        -: 3882:the input string may optionally be prefixed with C<"0x"> or plain C<"x">
